{"tid":922060,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（道德？）覺唔覺基因改造有副作用唔算可怕，無副作用先係最可怕","createTime":"2018-11-30T05:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T09:45:17.000Z","uid":49163,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"487f050698b44c7801b3b477b1c4da1e6856e8d8","tid":922060,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:04:50.000Z","msg":"如果有一日技術研發到基因改造無副作用<br />\n<br />\n人人都可以選擇自己子女既基因，個個都人造人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然可以排除d疾病進化人類，美好社會<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解有種好噁心不道德既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e97b4eab6ff72b897eea500f2c53f893956ebc3","tid":922060,"uid":197920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"487f050698b44c7801b3b477b1c4da1e6856e8d8","tid":922060,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:04:50.000Z","msg":"如果有一日技術研發到基因改造無副作用<br />\n<br />\n人人都可以選擇自己子女既基因，個個都人造人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然可以排除d疾病進化人類，美好社會<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解有種好噁心不道德既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"其實基因改造去治療疾病<br />\n唔係咩新鮮事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nThe procedure, pioneered by a team of researchers at the U.K.&rsquo;s Newcastle University, can be done a couple different ways. In the first, maternal spindle transfer, the nucleus is taken from a mother&rsquo;s egg and inserted into the donor egg, which has been cleared of everything but its mitochondria. The resulting egg&mdash;which contains nuclear DNA from one woman, mitochondrial DNA from another&mdash;is then fertilized with the father&rsquo;s sperm. <br />\n<br />\n美國有用人工方法將三個人既基因合埋<br />\n去防止一種由線粒體缺乏產生既疾病<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.theatlantic.com/amp/article/385126/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A